<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mening Ta'lim Platformam</title>
    <style>
        /* Umumiy sozlamalar */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        /* Chap menyu (Sidebar) */
        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .sidebar h2 {
            padding: 0 20px;
            color: #282a35;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .sidebar a {
            display: block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover {
            background-color: #e7e9eb;
        }

        .sidebar a.active {
            background-color: #04AA6D;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Asosiy kontent qismi */
        .main-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #04AA6D;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* "Try it Yourself" tugmasi kabi stillar */
        .btn-try {
            background-color: #04AA6D;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-try:hover {
            background-color: #059862;
        }

        /* Kod namunasi uchun blok */
        .code-box {
            background-color: #e7e9eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #04AA6D;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="sidebar">
        <h2>HTML Darslari</h2>
        <a href="#" class="active">Kirish</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Tahrirlagichlar</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Asoslari</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Elementlari</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Atributlari</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Sarlavhalar</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Paragraflar</a>
        <a href="#">HTML Stillar</a>
    </div>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>HTML Kirish</h1>
        </div>

        <p>HTML (HyperText Markup Language) — bu veb-sahifalarni yaratish uchun standart belgilash tili.</p>
        
        <h3>Oddiy HTML hujjati:</h3>
        
        <div class="code-box">
            &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;<br>
            &lt;html&gt;<br>
            &lt;head&gt;<br>
            &lt;title&gt;Sahifa nomi&lt;/title&gt;<br>
            &lt;/head&gt;<br>
            &lt;body&gt;<br>
            <br>
            &lt;h1&gt;Bu sarlavha&lt;/h1&gt;<br>
            &lt;p&gt;Bu paragraf.&lt;/p&gt;<br>
            <br>
            &lt;/body&gt;<br>
            &lt;/html&gt;
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="btn-try">O'zingiz sinab ko'ring &raquo;</a>

        <hr>

        <h2>HTML nima?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML "Hyper Text Markup Language" degan ma'noni anglatadi.</li>
            <li>HTML veb-sahifaning strukturasini tasvirlaydi.</li>
            <li>HTML bir qator elementlardan iborat.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
